        "created_at": "2018-09-30T17:25:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>10 years minimum\u2014which, in the premox era, was safe. No longer so. Hedge bets and drink half young, half aged.   And avoid bad producers\u2014Matrot in Perri\u00e8res, for example.</p>\n<p>Nice note.</p>",
